.c-choose
  .o-container
    .c-choose__content
      h2.heading--secondary Why choose Easybank?
      p.c-choose__description We leverage Open Banking to turn your bank account into your financial hub. Control your finances like never before.
    .c-features
      .c-feature
        .c-feature__icon
          img(src="images/icon-online.svg", alt="icon online")
        h2.c-feature__title Online Banking
        p.c-feature__description Our modern web and mobile applications allow you to keep track of your finances wherever you are in the world.

      .c-feature
        .c-feature__icon
          img(src="images/icon-budgeting.svg", alt="icon budgeting")
        h2.c-feature__title Simple Budgeting
        p.c-feature__description See exactly where your money goes each month. Receive notifications when you’re close to hitting your limits.

      .c-feature
        .c-feature__icon
          img(src="images/icon-onboarding.svg", alt="icon onboarding")
        h2.c-feature__title Fast Onboarding
        p.c-feature__description We don’t do branches. Open your account in minutes online and start taking control of your finances right away.

      .c-feature
        .c-feature__icon
          img(src="images/icon-api.svg", alt="icon api")
        h2.c-feature__title Open API
        p.c-feature__description Manage your savings, investments, pension, and much more from one account. Tracking your money has never been easier.